      "span_text": "Full-thickness human skin biopsies were obtained from sun-protected buttock skin of each subject by punch biopsy, as previously described. [CITATION_1] 45 All procedures involving human patients were conducted in accordance with the regulations set forth by the University of Michigan Institutional Review Board, and all patients provided written informed consent."
